# 2p_crouch_prone — host. Verifies ANIM_CROUCH and ANIM_PRONE sync
# correctly across the network. Host stands still; client cycles
# stand → crouch → stand → prone → stand. Both windows should render
# matching poses for the client mech at each timestamp.
#
# Map: aurora — west hill peak has open sky with clear visibility
# (no parallax cloud overlay). Spawn both mechs on the flat valley
# floor between the two hills, far enough apart that the camera shows
# both clearly.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/2p_crouch_prone_host
network host 24201
name HostA
loadout - "Pulse Rifle" "Sidearm" Light Standard
map aurora

# Host stands on the valley floor. Client to the right.
spawn_at 1500 2700
peer_spawn 1 1700 2700
aim 1700 2700

# Take screenshots at each pose state. Times match client script.
at 200 shot t200_both_standing
at 280 shot t280_client_crouching
at 360 shot t360_client_standing
at 440 shot t440_client_prone
at 520 shot t520_client_standing
at 580 end
